    Bundler choice (webpack vs vite): per the empirical finding, the exemplar uses `webpack.config.js`. Follow that. If the exemplar has been migrated to vite by the time this task runs, mirror whichever bundler is canonical at execution time — do not introduce divergence.

    Auth wiring is deliberately deferred to task 031 to keep this scaffold task in STANDARD rigor (no auth-sensitive code). The `src/auth/` placeholder dir + README anchor the slot for 031.
